<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c1">" لا يعرف"</span>. <span class="c1">"اللسان"</span> <span class="c2">(٥/ ٢٦٤)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
